narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned a lot about the history and social impact the Olympics and Olympic revival has on society.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The professor is easy to talk to and as such makes discussion valuable and very fruitful. He gives good feedback on essays and guides you to correct your mistakes on the next essay.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes because it teaches you a lot about yourself and your innate philosophy of sports as brought up by society.
